            "text": "<h3>Returns are issued on a case by case basis, and all sales are final. Any return or cancellation request can only be issued once the item arrives at the customers adress.</h3><h3>We have a 30-day return policy, which means you have 30 days after receiving your item to request a return. <br/><br/>To be eligible for a return, your item must be in the same condition that you received it, unworn or unused, with tags, and in its original packaging. You’ll also need the receipt or proof of purchase. <br/><br/>To start a return, you can contact us at <a href=\"mailto:londonnocturnal@gmail.com\">londonnocturnal@gmail.com</a>. Please note that returns will need to be sent to the following address: 31 Bridgewater Road, HP4 1HN, Berkhamsted, UK<br/></h3><h3><strong>Contact Us</strong> If you have any questions about our policy or your order, please reach out to us at our Instagram - nocturn.ldn or londonnocturnal@gmail.com</h3>"
